item.title: Orical X Server compiler
item.dc:creator: @TempahScape TempahScape
item.description:
@TempahScape wrote:

You see where it says the directory com/sun/tools/javac/main? Well go to that directory through java in program files, if that doesn’t work then right click the compiler, click edit and change the jdk thing to yours

Hope I helped you and good luck!
